data.shownotes: The legendary inaugural Goosemas event. Jon bought dozens of pizzas, trays of tenders, salad, and more, and maybe ten or twelve kegs. Bonnie and a good friend held down the bar. Thresher, Galardi, and others helped Coach set up in the basement of the studio. Goose played three sets...and the rest is history.
